author: admin
title: Cadence Announces Third Quarter 2015 Financial Results Webcast
text:
Cadence Design Systems, Inc. 
SAN JOSE, Calif., Oct. 9, 2015 /PRNewswire/ -- 
WHO: Cadence Design Systems, Inc. (NASDAQ: CDNS) to announce third quarter 2015 financial results via webcast. 
WHAT: You are invited to attend the third quarter 2015 financial results audio webcast. Participating on the webcast will be Lip-Bu Tan, president and chief executive officer, and Geoff Ribar, senior vice president and chief financial officer. 
WHEN: The webcast will begin Monday, Oct. 26, 2015 at 2 p.m. (Pacific)/5 p.m. (Eastern). An archive of the webcast will be available from 5 p.m. (Pacific) Oct. 26 until 5 p.m. (Pacific) Dec. 18, 2015. 
WHERE: The webcast will be available online at: http://www.cadence.com/cadence/investor_relations 
For more information, please contact: Therese Papenfuss
